<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Post Update — Amebo Naija</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f4; color: #1a1a1a; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background-color: #16a34a; padding: 40px 40px 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
    .header .logo span { color: #bbf7d0; }
    .header .tagline { font-size: 13px; color: #bbf7d0; margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b45309 0%, #d97706 50%, #f59e0b 100%); padding: 36px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .hero .emoji { font-size: 48px; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; line-height: 1.3; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #fde68a; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .body p { font-size: 15px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .body p strong { color: #d97706; }
    .post-card { background-color: #fffbeb; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0; border-left: 4px solid #d97706; }
    .post-card .label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #d97706; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .post-card .post-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #92400e; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .post-card .post-meta { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; }
    .tips { background-color: #f0fdf4; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0; border-left: 4px solid #16a34a; }
    .tips .label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #16a34a; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .tip-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .tip-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .tip-icon { font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }
    .tip-text { font-size: 14px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.5; }
    .cta-wrapper { text-align: center; margin: 32px 0 8px; }
    .cta-btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #16a34a; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; padding: 14px 40px; border-radius: 50px; letter-spacing: 0.3px; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.35); }
    .divider { height: 1px; background-color: #e5e7eb; margin: 32px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 28px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .footer p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .footer a { color: #16a34a; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
    .footer .social { margin: 14px 0 10px; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 6px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">Amebo<span>Naija</span></div>
      <div class="tagline">Nigeria's #1 Gist Hub</div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero">
      <span class="emoji">📋</span>
      <h1>Post update for <span><%= firstName %></span></h1>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p>
        Hi <strong><%= firstName %></strong>, thank you for submitting your post to Amebo Naija. After review, our admin team was unable to approve this post at this time.
      </p>

      <div class="post-card">
        <p class="label">Submitted Post</p>
        <p class="post-title">📝 <%= postTitle %></p>
        <p class="post-meta">Category: <%= category %> &nbsp;·&nbsp; Status: Not approved</p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Don't be discouraged — this happens to many writers. Here are some tips to help your next post get approved:
      </p>

      <div class="tips">
        <p class="label">Tips for approval</p>
        <div class="tip-item">
          <span class="tip-icon">✅</span>
          <span class="tip-text">Make sure your content is original and not copied from another site</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tip-item">
          <span class="tip-icon">✅</span>
          <span class="tip-text">Use a clear, engaging headline that reflects the content</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tip-item">
          <span class="tip-icon">✅</span>
          <span class="tip-text">Avoid offensive or misleading language</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tip-item">
          <span class="tip-icon">✅</span>
          <span class="tip-text">Add a cover image and relevant tags to your post</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tip-item">
          <span class="tip-icon">✅</span>
          <span class="tip-text">Write at least 150 words — short posts are less likely to be approved</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>
        You can edit your post and resubmit it from your dashboard. We look forward to reading your next gist!
      </p>

      <div class="cta-wrapper">
        <a href="https://amebonaija.vercel.app/dashboard/my-posts" class="cta-btn">Go to My Posts →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
        You're receiving this email because you submitted a post on Amebo Naija.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="social">🇳🇬</div>
      <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Amebo Naija. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><a href="https://amebonaija.vercel.app">amebonaija.vercel.app</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>